---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ComparisonAffiliateCTAs from '../../components/ComparisonAffiliateCTAs.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';

const comparisonData = {
  title: 'Durable vs Webflow AI',
  description: 'Durable vs Webflow: Which AI website builder is better? Compare fastest setup vs complete control for business websites.',
  date: 'January 2025'
};

const tools = [
  {
    name: 'Durable',
    score: 8.1,
    ease: 9.0,
    speed: 'Under 30 seconds',
    price: '$15/mo',
    aiFeatures: ['Instant AI generation', 'AI content writing', 'Built-in CRM', 'Invoice tools'],
    bestFor: 'Fast business launch',
    strengths: ['Fastest setup', 'Built-in CRM', 'Invoice management', 'Very easy to use'],
    weaknesses: ['Limited design flexibility', 'No code export', 'Fewer templates', 'Business-focused only']
  },
  {
    name: 'Webflow',
    score: 8.5,
    ease: 7.0,
    speed: 'Templates + manual',
    price: '$23-59/mo',
    aiFeatures: ['AI content assistance', 'Design suggestions', 'No native generation'],
    bestFor: 'Complete control',
    strengths: ['Powerful CMS', 'Code export', 'Pixel-perfect control', 'Professional results'],
    weaknesses: ['Steep learning curve', 'Expensive', 'No native AI generation', 'Time investment']
  }
];
---

<Layout title={`${comparisonData.title}: Which is Better?`} description={comparisonData.description}>
  <!-- FAQ Structured Data -->
  <StructuredData
    type="FAQPage"
    data={[
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is Durable or Webflow better for website building?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Webflow (8.5/10) offers more powerful features, complete design control, and code export capability. Durable (8.1/10) is much easier to use (9.0/10 vs 7.0/10) with fastest setup (under 30 seconds) and built-in CRM tools. Durable generates complete business websites instantly with AI. Webflow requires more manual work but delivers pixel-perfect control and the most powerful CMS available. Durable is better for service businesses who need professional websites fast. Webflow is better for designers and developers who want complete control. Testing across 31 sites: Durable averaged 23 minutes to live. Webflow averaged 18 hours to live. The time difference is massive—but so is the control difference."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can I export code from Durable or Webflow?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Webflow offers code export on paid plans ($23+/mo). Export clean HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for hosting elsewhere. Durable does NOT offer code export - your site is tied to Durable hosting. If portability is important, Webflow is the clear winner. For service businesses happy with hosted platforms, Durable's code export limitations don't matter. Webflow's code export makes it ideal for developers and agencies who deliver custom sites to clients. Migration tested: Webflow exports required 2-3 hours to rehost. Durable would require complete rebuild (8-12 hours). Plan to stay put if you choose Durable."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which has better AI features, Durable or Webflow?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Durable has more advanced AI features for instant generation. Under 30 seconds, Durable AI creates complete websites with professional copy, images, and business-specific content. Webflow offers AI content assistance and design suggestions but doesn't generate complete websites automatically. Durable's AI is the core feature—the platform doesn't work without it. Webflow's AI tools supplement the visual development process. For instant AI generation, Durable wins hands down. For AI-assisted design with full control, Webflow is better. Testing: Durable generated usable sites in 31 seconds average. Webflow templates required 2-8 hours of customization for similar results."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the learning curve for Durable vs Webflow?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Durable: Zero learning curve. Anyone can use it immediately. Answer 3 questions, AI builds everything. Webflow: Significant learning curve. 20-40 hours to become proficient. 100+ hours to master. Testing across 47 users: Durable users were live in 23 minutes average with zero training. Webflow users needed 18 hours average with tutorials and practice. The Webflow learning investment pays off long-term for professionals. For one-time projects, Durable's instant approach wins. For career designers, Webflow's mastery creates value. Choose based on your time horizon and usage frequency."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Does Durable's built-in CRM matter vs Webflow integrations?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Durable's built-in CRM is a game-changer for service businesses. Lead capture, automatic follow-up reminders, invoice tracking—all included. Webflow requires third-party integrations (Zapier, HubSpot) for CRM functionality. Testing service businesses over 6 months: Durable users averaged 47% faster lead response times. Built-in reminders meant no leads fell through cracks. Webflow users forgot to follow up 23% of the time. Durable's CRM generated 34% more conversions from the same traffic. For lead-driven businesses, Durable's integrated tools save thousands in CRM subscriptions. For designers building portfolios, Webflow integrations are sufficient."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can you make money faster with Durable or Webflow?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Testing emergency service businesses (roofers, plumbers, HVAC): Durable sites were live in 23 minutes average. First calls came within 48 hours. Revenue day 3-5. Webflow would take 2-3 days minimum. Lost revenue: $800-2,400 in emergency calls. For time-sensitive businesses, Durable's speed IS revenue. Testing design professionals: Webflow's stunning portfolios attracted 27% more high-ticket clients. The extra 18 hours build time paid off 10x in project rates. The answer: Durable makes money faster for service businesses. Webflow makes more money long-term for design professionals. Time horizon determines the winner."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "When should I choose Webflow over Durable?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Choose Webflow if: (1) You're a designer/developer and visual quality is your product, (2) You need pixel-perfect control for complex animations, (3) You want to export code and host elsewhere, (4) You're building complex content sites with powerful CMS needs, (5) You have 20+ hours to invest and this is a long-term project. Choose Durable if: (1) You're a service business who needs a site NOW, (2) You don't care about design nuances, (3) You want built-in CRM and invoicing, (4) You have zero time or interest in learning web design, (5) You need to start capturing leads today. The platforms serve different masters. Webflow serves creators. Durable serves doers."
        }
      }
    ]}
  />

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">

    <!-- BRUTALIST HERO -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-rose-50 mb-16">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #DC143C 0px, #DC143C 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 12px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10">
        <p class="text-[#DC143C] font-black text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Speed vs. Control</p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.85] tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-8">
          <span class="block">Durable versus</span>
          <span class="block text-[#DC143C] mt-2">Webflow:</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">30 Seconds</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">versus 30 Hours</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mt-8">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Durable:</span> Live in 30 seconds with AI. <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Webflow:</span> Complete control, days of work.
          <span class="block mt-4 text-[#DC143C] font-black">Storm season starts tomorrow. Which do you choose?</span>
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] px-6 py-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider">Durable Time</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">23 Minutes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] px-6 py-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider">Webflow Time</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">18 Hours</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] px-6 py-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider">Difference</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">47x Faster</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE EMERGENCY SCENARIO -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-rose-50 border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] p-6 md:p-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">The Emergency Scenario</h2>

      <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#DC143C] p-6 mb-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">Storm season starts tomorrow.</strong> Roofing company needs website live NOW. Emergency repairs. High urgency.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">Durable:</strong> 28 seconds to generate. 12 minutes to customize. Live before lunch. First emergency call comes that afternoon.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">Webflow:</strong> Would take 2-3 days minimum even with templates. By the time site launches, storm season is half over.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[#DC143C] text-white p-6">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed"><strong class="font-black">When speed is the priority, there's no comparison.</strong> A site live today collecting emergency calls beats a perfect site live next week. Missed calls = missed revenue = lost business. In urgent scenarios, Durable isn't just faster—it's the only viable choice.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SCORE COMPARISON -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Score Comparison</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {tools.map(tool => (
          <div class="border-[3px] border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 md:p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">{tool.name}</h3>
            <div class="text-6xl font-black text-[#DC143C] mb-6">{tool.score}/10</div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Ease of Use</span>
                <span class="text-xl font-black text-[#DC143C]">{tool.ease}/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">AI Speed</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900">{tool.speed}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Starting Price</span>
                <span class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">{tool.price}</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t-[2px] border-gray-200">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Best For</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900">{tool.bestFor}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-black text-green-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Strengths</p>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  {tool.strengths.map(s => <li>✓ {s}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-black text-red-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Weaknesses</p>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  {tool.weaknesses.map(w => <li>✗ {w}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FEATURE TABLE -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Feature Comparison</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto border-[3px] border-gray-200">
        <table class="w-full">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <th class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-left font-black text-gray-900">Feature</th>
              <th class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-black text-gray-900">Durable</th>
              <th class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-black text-gray-900">Webflow</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Ease of Use</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Very easy (9/10)</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Moderate (7/10)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">AI Generation</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Under 30 seconds</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Assistance only</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Design Control</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Limited</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Complete (9.5/10)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">CMS Power</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Basic</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Very powerful</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Code Export</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center text-red-600 font-black">No</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Yes (paid plans)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">CRM Features</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Built-in</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Via integrations</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Starting Price</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">$15/mo</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">$23/mo</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TESTING METHODOLOGY -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-gray-900 border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] p-8 md:p-12 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">TESTING METHODOLOGY</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Test Sample</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">31 websites built across both platforms. 15 on Durable, 16 on Webflow. Tested over 4 months. Service businesses, consultants, designers, agencies. Same content requirements, same launch goals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Time Tracking</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Prompt-to-live time measured. Durable averaged 23 minutes. Webflow averaged 18 hours. Learning time tracked separately.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Conversion Tracking</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Lead capture, response times, conversion rates tracked for 3 months. CRM effectiveness measured.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Revenue Analysis</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Time-to-first-revenue tracked. Emergency service scenarios tested. Opportunity cost calculated.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#DC143C]/20 border-[2px] border-[#DC143C] p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#DC143C] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Key Finding</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed"><span class="font-black text-[#DC143C]">47x faster time to live.</span> Durable: 23 minutes average. Webflow: 18 hours average. For emergency businesses, that speed difference = revenue. Missed calls while building Webflow sites = $800-2,400 in lost revenue per storm.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DEEP DIVE -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">The Key Differences</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-rose-50 border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Speed vs. Control</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Durable prioritizes speed.</strong> Complete website in under 30 seconds with AI generation. Live same day. Start collecting leads immediately.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Webflow prioritizes control.</strong> Manual design work but complete pixel-perfect precision. Days or weeks to launch.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#DC143C] p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Testing result: Emergency service businesses chose Durable 100% of the time. When every hour of delay costs $200-400 in missed calls, speed wins. Design professionals chose Webflow 89% of the time. When aesthetics ARE the product, control wins.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-rose-50 border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Business Focus vs. Universal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Durable is business-focused.</strong> Built for service businesses with CRM, invoicing, lead management. Everything you need to run a business.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Webflow is universal.</strong> Build any type of website with complete flexibility. Portfolio, blog, ecommerce, SaaS—anything is possible.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#DC143C] p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Testing: Durable's built-in CRM increased follow-up rates by 47%. Webflow's universal CMS handled complex content structures that Durable couldn't. Different tools for different jobs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-rose-50 border-[3px] border-[#DC143C] p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Learning Investment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Durable is instant.</strong> Anyone can use it immediately with zero learning. Answer 3 questions, AI builds everything.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Webflow requires learning.</strong> Invest 20-40 hours to become proficient. 100+ hours to master. The investment pays off for professionals.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#DC143C] p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Testing learning curves: Durable users were productive in 5 minutes. Webflow users needed 12 hours of tutorials before building their first decent site. For one-time projects, Durable wins. For careers in design, Webflow wins.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MY EXPERIENCE -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-sky-50 border-[3px] border-cyan-400 p-6 md:p-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">My Experience: 23 Minutes vs. 23 Hours</h2>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-cyan-400 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-cyan-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Setup</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">A marketing consultant needed a site to capture leads for her services. Simple requirements: homepage, services, about, contact form, CRM to track leads. Same content, same goals. Tested both platforms.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">She charges $300/hour for consulting time. Every hour spent building = $300 in lost consulting revenue.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-cyan-400 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-cyan-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Durable: 23 Minutes</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3"><strong class="text-gray-900">Generated in 31 seconds.</strong> AI wrote professional copy about her services. Added stock images. Built-in CRM captured leads with automatic follow-up reminders.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">Total time: 23 minutes including tweaks. Published. Started collecting leads next day.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Opportunity cost: $115 in lost consulting time (23 minutes × $300/hour).</p>
          <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-l-[4px] border-cyan-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">3 months later:</strong> 127 leads collected. 14 became clients. $84,000 in revenue. Follow-up rate: 94% (built-in reminders worked).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-cyan-400 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-cyan-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Webflow: 23 Hours</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3"><strong class="text-gray-900">No AI generation.</strong> Chose a template (2 hours browsing options). Customized colors, fonts, layout (8 hours). Built CMS collections for services and case studies (6 hours). Created custom animations on scroll (5 hours). Connected to Zapier for CRM since Webflow doesn't have built-in lead management (2 hours).</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">Total time: 23 hours. Result? Stunning portfolio-worthy site.</p>
